Text: FW SG Interview ConfirmationOriginal Message From mailto Sent Tuesday December PM To Subject SG Interview Confirmation Brad You are scheduled to interview tomorow with Societe Generale at PM You will be interviewing with Francois Thiery and Pascal Guillot Pascal is the head of trading for the Americas and Francous is his head of trading The videoconference will be held at the following address Southloop West Suite Houston If it goes well they will fly you up for a formal interview Regards Craig Jefferies President CKB Energy Inc
